The paper discusses strategies and a novel deep learning architecture to achieve safety and security of AI, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also explores ways to guard AI from adversaries, which is related to computer security (cs.CR). The use of visual similarity and sequence analysis suggests a connection to computer vision (cs.CV), while the overall goal of achieving reliable and safe AI could also be relevant to systems and control (cs.SY).
